OL,3,CScramblers causing 'huge concern' as
OL,4,Cpublic urged to report dangerous use
OL,6,FScramblers are causing "huge concern"
OL,7,Fand "annoyance" in communities in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland, police have said as
OL,9,Fthey warned of the dangers of using
OL,10,Fthem unsafely ahead of Christmas.
OL,12,FThe PSNI has asked people to report
OL,13,Fthe illegal and dangerous riding of
OL,14,Fscramblers over the festive period.
OL,16,FThey said officers would be on patrol
OL,17,Fto detect people not using scramblers
OL,18,Fin the right area or with the right
OL,19,Fequipment.
