OL,6,FA senior officer said they were
OL,7,Fworking on a long-term solution to
OL,8,Ffind a dedicated scrambler site in
OL,9,FBelfast.
OL,11,F"Scramblers, used illegally, are not
OL,12,Ftoys," Constable William Kingsberry
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"They are powerful machines that can
OL,16,Fcause serious injury, damage community-
OL,17,Fuse spaces, result in a criminal
OL,18,Fconviction and even be fatal.
