OL,3,CScramblers causing 'huge concern' as
OL,4,Cpublic urged to report dangerous use
OL,6,F"We know scramblers are causing huge
OL,7,Fconcern within our community through
OL,8,Fannoyance and disruption.
OL,10,F"What also worries us is that they are
OL,11,Fa big risk to the safety of both
OL,12,Friders and the public, and I fear that
OL,13,Fsomeone is going to be seriously hurt
OL,14,Fas a result of their use.
OL,16,F"We want everyone to enjoy a safe and
OL,17,Fpeaceful Christmas.
