OL,3,CScramblers causing 'huge concern' as
OL,4,Cpublic urged to report dangerous use
OL,6,F"Please help make our roads and
OL,7,Fcommunities safe spaces for all by
OL,8,Fmaking responsible, safe decisions
OL,9,Fthis festive season."
OL,11,FThere has been a reduction in
OL,12,Fscrambler-related incidents in west
OL,13,FBelfast and across the city, with a
OL,14,F29.8% reduction in incidents from the
OL,15,Fwinter period of 2023 to the winter of
OL,16,F2024.
OL,18,FThe PSNI recently set up an initiative
OL,19,Fto provide safe scrambling courses to
OL,20,Fcommunities and young people.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@UO]
