OL,3,CScramblers causing 'huge concern' as
OL,4,Cpublic urged to report dangerous use
OL,6,F"We are working closely with Belfast
OL,7,FCity Council to try and identify a
OL,8,Fsuitable location for a dedicated
OL,9,Fscrambler site with the outcome of a
OL,10,Ffeasibility study to be published
OL,11,Fearly next year," Con Kingsberry said.
OL,13,F"We view a permanent site as a
OL,14,Fprogressive solution to this problem.
OL,16,F"This work is really encouraging and
OL,17,Fwe don't want to lose momentum here.
