OL,3,CScramblers causing 'huge concern' as
OL,4,Cpublic urged to report dangerous use
OL,6,F"We know the dangerous driving of
OL,7,Fscramblers and other off-road bikes
OL,8,Fremains a key concern in the
OL,9,Fcommunity. We want to reassure you,
OL,10,Fit's one we take seriously.
OL,12,F"To anyone thinking about getting on
OL,13,Fone of these vehicles this Christmas,
OL,14,Fwe urge them to think about where it
OL,15,Fis going to be used and the potential
OL,16,Fdisruption and damage you could be
OL,17,Fcausing to your own community.
OL,19,F"We will have targeted patrolling in
OL,20,Fplace and will be detecting offenders.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU{D@AOU
