OL,3,CScramblers causing 'huge concern' as
OL,4,Cpublic urged to report dangerous use
OL,6,F"Some scramblers do not comply with
OL,7,FConstruction and Use Regulations and
OL,8,FVehicle Safety Standards and therefore
OL,9,Fare restricted to 'off-road' use only.
OL,11,F"This does not mean that they can be
OL,12,Fdriven anywhere off-road. These
OL,13,Fvehicles should only be driven on
OL,14,Fprivate land where the landowner has
OL,15,Fgiven permission and should not be
OL,16,Fdriven on pavements, roads, public
OL,17,Fproperty or parks.
OL,19,F"Insurance and safety equipment must
OL,20,Fbe complied with as well in order to
OL,21,Fdrive these vehicles legally.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU{D@AOU
