OL,3,CScramblers causing 'huge concern' as
OL,4,Cpublic urged to report dangerous use
OL,6,F"We'd also ask that the community
OL,7,Fcontinues to report the illegal and
OL,8,Fdangerous driving of these bikes so we
OL,9,Fcan help make our roads and parks
OL,10,Fsafer for everyone.
OL,12,F"Call us on 101 or report online at
OL,13,Fwww.psni.police.uk/report. If you want
OL,14,Fto anonymously provide us with
OL,15,Finformation on those responsible for
OL,16,Fthis nuisance in our community, you
OL,17,Fcan do so via the charity
OL,18,FCrimestoppers, which gives you the
OL,19,Fpower to speak up and stop crime.
